com.inqwell.any.client

Class ListRenderInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inqwell.any.AbstractAny
      • com.inqwell.any.client.ListRenderInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Any, RenderInfo, Serializable

    public class ListRenderInfo
extends AbstractAny
implements RenderInfo
    Support for the rendering of lists whose visible (or external) representation may be different from the internal value.

    $Revision: 1.4 $
    Author:
    $Author: sanderst $
